rows.label: tlk70000056_05_msg0001
rows.name: Are you guys really gonna go fight?

rows.label: tlk70000056_05_msg0002
rows.name:
You're gonna come back real soon,
right? You're not going to disappear,
or d...die on me, are you?

rows.label: tlk70000056_05_msg0003
rows.name:
I'm gonna be a Driver when I'm big.
So I have lots of stuff I wanna talk to
you guys about.

rows.label: tlk70000056_05_msg0004
rows.name:
Me and da and Kei'll be waiting
here when you get back, kay?

rows.label: tlk70000056_05_msg0005
rows.name: Saying goodbye is the worst. I hate it.
